platformAttributes.ios.editorialNotes.st.k: This fun brain-bender takes the winning WordBrain formula to another level. Trace adjoining tiles to spell words long and short, each organized into categories that point your gray cells in the right direction. But you’ll have to spell carefully, because the order of the letters you choose determines whether you can clear the board. It’s a zippy spin on time-tested gameplay—and a perfect fit for puzzle fans.
